data.description: An adorable perfect sized home to cute to be true! Sellers relocating out of state and wish they could take their home with them. Rosewood Estates is situated perfectly in Azle and in a great school district. Everything you need is minutes away. This quaint 3 beds 2 bath home is well cared for and also has an office which is hard to find in a home this size. Brick with stone accents and dark trim wood makes the curb appeal super nice. All electric home with    appliances. Perfect sized back yard for family or pets will be easy to maintain. Just minutes to the gorgeous Eagle Mountain Lake for more family fun and just 15 minutes to downtown Fort Worth.
